59
00:04:29,899 --> 00:04:31,499
Dia bukan kau, Genta.

60
00:04:31,499 --> 00:04:33,799
Yah, kita mulai lagi.

61
00:04:35,699 --> 00:04:37,699
"Kantor Detektif Mouri"

62
00:04:41,499 --> 00:04:44,599
Astaga...

63
00:04:44,599 --> 00:04:47,499
