186
00:10:50,699 --> 00:10:52,899
aku disuruh untuk datang kapan saja.

187
00:10:52,899 --> 00:10:55,699
Aku sungguh menantikan untuk bertemu dia.

188
00:10:55,699 --> 00:10:57,299
Ya, begitu juga aku.

189
00:11:02,699 --> 00:11:04,999
Permisi. Ini aku, Haruna.

190
00:11:04,999 --> 00:11:08,299
Ya. Silahkan masuk.

191
00:11:09,599 --> 00:11:10,999
"Kazuko Ogata (50), istri Tsuneo" -Oh astaga,

192
00:11:10,999 --> 00:11:14,099
